"{\"uid\": \"standard.co.uk-sport-sport-olympics-louie-hinchliffe-100m-paris-olympics-2024-team-gb-b1174196.html\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"To use the search feature, we need your consent to load Google Custom Search, which may use cookies or similar technologies.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 124, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 56, \"end\": 76, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_Programmable_Search_Engine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Google Custom Search\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_Programmable_Search_Engine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_Programmable_Search_Engine\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the search feature\", \"from\": 7, \"to\": 25}, {\"ngram\": \"your consent\", \"from\": 35, \"to\": 47}, {\"ngram\": \"cookies\", \"from\": 92, \"to\": 99}, {\"ngram\": \"similar technologies\", \"from\": 103, \"to\": 123}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Please click 'Allow and Continue' below to enable search.\", \"from\": 125, \"to\": 182, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"search\", \"from\": 175, \"to\": 181}]}, {\"sentence\": \"See our privacy policy for more information.\", \"from\": 183, \"to\": 227, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"our privacy policy\", \"from\": 187, \"to\": 205}, {\"ngram\": \"more information\", \"from\": 210, \"to\": 226}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Sport|Olympics Louie Hinchliffe is very laid-back, to the extent that he arrived on the Eurostar into Paris unaware what day he was actually competing in the 100m at theOlympics.\", \"from\": 229, \"to\": 408, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 245, \"end\": 250, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pikmin\", \"score\": 0.9999999997812665, \"rank\": 2.1878553952880415e-10, \"text\": \"Louie\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pikmin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pikmin\"}, {\"begin\": 318, \"end\": 326, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eurostar\", \"score\": 0.9999998555113156, \"rank\": 1.4448891598108213e-07, \"text\": \"Eurostar\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eurostar\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eurostar\"}, {\"begin\": 332, \"end\": 337, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.936798585060656e-14, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the extent\", \"from\": 283, \"to\": 293}, {\"ngram\": \"the 100m\", \"from\": 383, \"to\": 391}, {\"ngram\": \"theOlympics\", \"from\": 395, \"to\": 406}]}, {\"sentence\": \"While his sprint rivals are usually amped up and talking their way to sprint glory, Hinchliffe is relaxed to the point it is occasionally maddening to coach Carl Lewis and the other support staff around him.\", \"from\": 410, \"to\": 617, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 567, \"end\": 577, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carl_Lewis\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Carl Lewis\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carl_Lewis\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carl_Lewis\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his sprint rivals\", \"from\": 416, \"to\": 433}, {\"ngram\": \"their way\", \"from\": 467, \"to\": 476}, {\"ngram\": \"glory\", \"from\": 487, \"to\": 492}, {\"ngram\": \"Hinchliffe\", \"from\": 494, \"to\": 504}, {\"ngram\": \"the point\", \"from\": 519, \"to\": 528}, {\"ngram\": \"the other support staff\", \"from\": 582, \"to\": 605}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But unlikeNoah Lyles's verbal diarrhoea en route to a double world title at the World Championships last year, the 22-year-old with the silent swagger has no plans to change his ways.\", \"from\": 619, \"to\": 802, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 634, \"end\": 639, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Lyles\", \"score\": 0.9925709335797056, \"rank\": 0.007484539869117379, \"text\": \"Lyles\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Lyles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Lyles\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"route\", \"from\": 662, \"to\": 667}, {\"ngram\": \"a double world title\", \"from\": 671, \"to\": 691}, {\"ngram\": \"the World Championships\", \"from\": 695, \"to\": 718}, {\"ngram\": \"the silent swagger\", \"from\": 751, \"to\": 769}, {\"ngram\": \"no plans\", \"from\": 774, \"to\": 782}, {\"ngram\": \"his ways\", \"from\": 793, \"to\": 801}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I think I will let my running do the talking,\\\" he said, with a smile.\", \"from\": 804, \"to\": 874, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my running\", \"from\": 824, \"to\": 834}, {\"ngram\": \"the talking\", \"from\": 838, \"to\": 849}, {\"ngram\": \"a smile\", \"from\": 866, \"to\": 873}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I do not need to trash-talk.\\\"\", \"from\": 875, \"to\": 905, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"As for his chilled demeanour, he admits that might need a tweak in Paris and beyond.\", \"from\": 907, \"to\": 991, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 974, \"end\": 979, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.936798585060656e-14, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his chilled demeanour\", \"from\": 914, \"to\": 935}, {\"ngram\": \"a tweak\", \"from\": 963, \"to\": 970}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"People say I need to be more switched on and not too relaxed,\\\" he said, although his body language does not suggest he is planning to change his ways any time soon.\", \"from\": 992, \"to\": 1157, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"People\", \"from\": 993, \"to\": 999}, {\"ngram\": \"his body language\", \"from\": 1074, \"to\": 1091}, {\"ngram\": \"his ways\", \"from\": 1134, \"to\": 1142}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In any case, he argues, he is switched on when he needs to be - and results seem to suggest he is going about things in the right way with such an easy-going approach.\", \"from\": 1159, \"to\": 1326, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"any case\", \"from\": 1162, \"to\": 1170}, {\"ngram\": \"results\", \"from\": 1227, \"to\": 1234}, {\"ngram\": \"things\", \"from\": 1269, \"to\": 1275}, {\"ngram\": \"the right way\", \"from\": 1279, \"to\": 1292}, {\"ngram\": \"such an easy-going approach\", \"from\": 1298, \"to\": 1325}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He has run the quickest time by a Briton in history, although his 9.84sec effort is not in the record books, because it was wind-assisted, but he still has a best official time of 9.95.\", \"from\": 1327, \"to\": 1512, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the quickest time\", \"from\": 1338, \"to\": 1355}, {\"ngram\": \"a Briton\", \"from\": 1359, \"to\": 1367}, {\"ngram\": \"history\", \"from\": 1371, \"to\": 1378}, {\"ngram\": \"his 9.84sec effort\", \"from\": 1389, \"to\": 1407}, {\"ngram\": \"the record books\", \"from\": 1418, \"to\": 1434}, {\"ngram\": \"a best official time\", \"from\": 1483, \"to\": 1503}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Prior to the start of this year, he was unheard of in sprinting circles, but is now a sub-10sec runner and the relatively recently crowned British champion.\", \"from\": 1514, \"to\": 1670, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1653, \"end\": 1669, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Figure_Skating_Championships\", \"score\": 0.999829204901502, \"rank\": 0.0001708242740625342, \"text\": \"British champion\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Figure_Skating_Championships\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Figure_Skating_Championships\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the start\", \"from\": 1523, \"to\": 1532}, {\"ngram\": \"this year\", \"from\": 1536, \"to\": 1545}, {\"ngram\": \"sprinting circles\", \"from\": 1568, \"to\": 1585}, {\"ngram\": \"a sub-10sec runner\", \"from\": 1598, \"to\": 1616}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And all of that rests on his decision to quit Lancaster University and relocate to Houston in Texas to work under nine-time Olympic champion Lewis, while continuing his studies in management and IT.\", \"from\": 1671, \"to\": 1869, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1717, \"end\": 1737, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lancaster_University\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Lancaster University\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q3918\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q2385804\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lancaster_University\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lancaster_University\"}, {\"begin\": 1754, \"end\": 1761, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Houston\", \"score\": 0.9998943091950473, \"rank\": 7.332582437581709e-05, \"text\": \"Houston\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Houston\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Houston\"}, {\"begin\": 1765, \"end\": 1770, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Texas_Longhorns\", \"score\": 0.7883953436025641, \"rank\": 0.2620990922633901, \"text\": \"Texas\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Texas_Longhorns\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Texas_Longhorns\"}, {\"begin\": 1812, \"end\": 1817, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lewis_gun\", \"score\": 0.7910237713643548, \"rank\": 0.26410251434153237, \"text\": \"Lewis\", \"types\": [\"Q728\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lewis_gun\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lewis_gun\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his decision\", \"from\": 1696, \"to\": 1708}, {\"ngram\": \"his studies\", \"from\": 1836, \"to\": 1847}, {\"ngram\": \"management\", \"from\": 1851, \"to\": 1861}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Lewis flew over to Manchester for his national title win at the end of June and has been in Paris to guide him amid his other duties, including carrying the Olympic torch on a speedboat down the River Seine, although looking terrified in doing so, much to his young charge's amusement.\", \"from\": 1871, \"to\": 2156, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1890, \"end\": 1900, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Manchester\", \"score\": 0.9999999780065993, \"rank\": 1.4768984913598282e-08, \"text\": \"Manchester\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Manchester\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Manchester\"}, {\"begin\": 1963, \"end\": 1968, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.936798585060656e-14, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 2066, \"end\": 2077, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"River Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Lewis\", \"from\": 1871, \"to\": 1876}, {\"ngram\": \"his national title win\", \"from\": 1905, \"to\": 1927}, {\"ngram\": \"the end\", \"from\": 1931, \"to\": 1938}, {\"ngram\": \"June\", \"from\": 1942, \"to\": 1946}, {\"ngram\": \"his other duties\", \"from\": 1987, \"to\": 2003}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic torch\", \"from\": 2024, \"to\": 2041}, {\"ngram\": \"a speedboat\", \"from\": 2045, \"to\": 2056}, {\"ngram\": \"his young charge's amusement\", \"from\": 2127, \"to\": 2155}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Explaining his own shift in pace this season, the Sheffield sprinter said: \\\"There is been multiple factors, but Carl's been a very big factor.\", \"from\": 2158, \"to\": 2300, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2208, \"end\": 2217, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sheffield\", \"score\": 0.999999999783995, \"rank\": 1.4725350848690895e-10, \"text\": \"Sheffield\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sheffield\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sheffield\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his own shift\", \"from\": 2169, \"to\": 2182}, {\"ngram\": \"pace\", \"from\": 2186, \"to\": 2190}, {\"ngram\": \"multiple factors\", \"from\": 2248, \"to\": 2264}, {\"ngram\": \"Carl\", \"from\": 2270, \"to\": 2274}, {\"ngram\": \"a very big factor\", \"from\": 2282, \"to\": 2299}]}, {\"sentence\": \"To be with a guy who's achieved what he's achieved, being surrounded by winners like him has helped push me on.\\\"\", \"from\": 2301, \"to\": 2413, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a guy\", \"from\": 2312, \"to\": 2317}, {\"ngram\": \"winners\", \"from\": 2373, \"to\": 2380}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Lewis has talked about being a variety of different things to Hinchliffe: a coach, part-father figure, older brother, confidant, sounding board and almost headmaster when needs must.\", \"from\": 2415, \"to\": 2597, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Lewis\", \"from\": 2415, \"to\": 2420}, {\"ngram\": \"a variety\", \"from\": 2444, \"to\": 2453}, {\"ngram\": \"different things\", \"from\": 2457, \"to\": 2473}, {\"ngram\": \"Hinchliffe\", \"from\": 2477, \"to\": 2487}, {\"ngram\": \"a coach\", \"from\": 2489, \"to\": 2496}, {\"ngram\": \"part-father figure\", \"from\": 2498, \"to\": 2516}, {\"ngram\": \"older brother\", \"from\": 2518, \"to\": 2531}, {\"ngram\": \"confidant\", \"from\": 2533, \"to\": 2542}, {\"ngram\": \"board\", \"from\": 2553, \"to\": 2558}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Describing Lewis's coaching approach, Hinchliffe said: \\\"I would say he's an arm around the shoulder coach, [someone] who cares for his athletes.\", \"from\": 2599, \"to\": 2743, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2610, \"end\": 2615, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lewis_gun\", \"score\": 0.7910237713643548, \"rank\": 0.26410251434153237, \"text\": \"Lewis\", \"types\": [\"Q728\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lewis_gun\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lewis_gun\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Hinchliffe\", \"from\": 2637, \"to\": 2647}, {\"ngram\": \"an arm\", \"from\": 2672, \"to\": 2678}, {\"ngram\": \"the shoulder coach\", \"from\": 2686, \"to\": 2704}, {\"ngram\": \"[someone\", \"from\": 2706, \"to\": 2714}, {\"ngram\": \"his athletes\", \"from\": 2730, \"to\": 2742}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Obviously, he's there if and when you are stepping out of line, and he will shout if needed, but it's not like he's ripping you to shreds.\", \"from\": 2744, \"to\": 2882, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"line\", \"from\": 2802, \"to\": 2806}, {\"ngram\": \"shreds\", \"from\": 2875, \"to\": 2881}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He shows a lot of compassion.\\\"\", \"from\": 2883, \"to\": 2913, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 2892, \"to\": 2897}, {\"ngram\": \"compassion\", \"from\": 2901, \"to\": 2911}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Should Hinchliffe ever brag about his results, which is not often, Lewis is apparently quick to bring up his own past successes should he need to, in order to put his own athletes' performances into perspective.\", \"from\": 2915, \"to\": 3126, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2982, \"end\": 2987, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lewis_gun\", \"score\": 0.7910237713643548, \"rank\": 0.26410251434153237, \"text\": \"Lewis\", \"types\": [\"Q728\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lewis_gun\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lewis_gun\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Hinchliffe\", \"from\": 2922, \"to\": 2932}, {\"ngram\": \"his results\", \"from\": 2949, \"to\": 2960}, {\"ngram\": \"his own past successes\", \"from\": 3020, \"to\": 3042}, {\"ngram\": \"order\", \"from\": 3065, \"to\": 3070}, {\"ngram\": \"his own athletes' performances\", \"from\": 3078, \"to\": 3108}, {\"ngram\": \"perspective\", \"from\": 3114, \"to\": 3125}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"With what he's done, he could be a lot more unlikeable and let it get to his head,\\\" said Hinchliffe.\", \"from\": 3127, \"to\": 3228, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his head\", \"from\": 3201, \"to\": 3209}, {\"ngram\": \"Hinchliffe\", \"from\": 3217, \"to\": 3227}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"He's very down to earth.\\\"\", \"from\": 3229, \"to\": 3255, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"earth\", \"from\": 3248, \"to\": 3253}]}, {\"sentence\": \"At the start of the year, Britain's new sprint sensation, who has been tipped to be one of Britain's best yet by his coach, even eclipsing former rival Linford Christie, said he had no expectation of making it to Paris.\", \"from\": 3257, \"to\": 3476, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3283, \"end\": 3290, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9999569914975197, \"rank\": 4.300665285893272e-05, \"text\": \"Britain\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}, {\"begin\": 3409, \"end\": 3425, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Linford_Christie\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Linford Christie\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Linford_Christie\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Linford_Christie\"}, {\"begin\": 3470, \"end\": 3475, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.936798585060656e-14, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the start\", \"from\": 3260, \"to\": 3269}, {\"ngram\": \"the year\", \"from\": 3273, \"to\": 3281}, {\"ngram\": \"his coach\", \"from\": 3370, \"to\": 3379}, {\"ngram\": \"no expectation\", \"from\": 3439, \"to\": 3453}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Aquatics GB 'immensely disappointed' as Proud joins Enhanced Games Sports quiz of 2024: 100 hard questions on an incredible year Keely Hodgkinson reveals Grand Slam Track decision and 2025 ambitions The best destinations and activities to book this winter \\\"Definitely not,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 3478, \"to\": 3764, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3609, \"end\": 3625, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keely_Hodgkinson\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Keely Hodgkinson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keely_Hodgkinson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keely_Hodgkinson\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Proud\", \"from\": 3518, \"to\": 3523}, {\"ngram\": \"Enhanced Games Sports quiz\", \"from\": 3530, \"to\": 3556}, {\"ngram\": \"100 hard questions\", \"from\": 3566, \"to\": 3584}, {\"ngram\": \"an incredible year\", \"from\": 3588, \"to\": 3606}, {\"ngram\": \"Grand Slam Track decision\", \"from\": 3632, \"to\": 3657}, {\"ngram\": \"2025 ambitions\", \"from\": 3662, \"to\": 3676}, {\"ngram\": \"The best destinations\", \"from\": 3677, \"to\": 3698}, {\"ngram\": \"activities\", \"from\": 3703, \"to\": 3713}, {\"ngram\": \"this winter\", \"from\": 3722, \"to\": 3733}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"But that was the intention in going to Houston.\", \"from\": 3765, \"to\": 3813, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3805, \"end\": 3812, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Houston\", \"score\": 0.9998943091950473, \"rank\": 7.332582437581709e-05, \"text\": \"Houston\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Houston\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Houston\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the intention\", \"from\": 3779, \"to\": 3792}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I was running nowhere near as fast last year, so it's exceeded my expectations to achieve what I have achieved.\\\"\", \"from\": 3814, \"to\": 3926, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my expectations\", \"from\": 3877, \"to\": 3892}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Does that allow him to dare to dream of a medal here in the 100m or go on to emulate his coach's prediction for him?\", \"from\": 3928, \"to\": 4044, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a medal\", \"from\": 3968, \"to\": 3975}, {\"ngram\": \"the 100m\", \"from\": 3984, \"to\": 3992}, {\"ngram\": \"his coach's prediction\", \"from\": 4013, \"to\": 4035}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I do not really have a target,\\\" he said of his event, which gets under way on Saturday.\", \"from\": 4045, \"to\": 4133, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a target\", \"from\": 4067, \"to\": 4075}, {\"ngram\": \"his event\", \"from\": 4089, \"to\": 4098}, {\"ngram\": \"way\", \"from\": 4117, \"to\": 4120}, {\"ngram\": \"Saturday\", \"from\": 4124, \"to\": 4132}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"A lot of people set targets for me, but I do not like to.\", \"from\": 4134, \"to\": 4192, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"A lot\", \"from\": 4135, \"to\": 4140}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 4144, \"to\": 4150}, {\"ngram\": \"targets\", \"from\": 4155, \"to\": 4162}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I just want to run against myself and leave the race with no regrets.\", \"from\": 4193, \"to\": 4262, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the race\", \"from\": 4237, \"to\": 4245}, {\"ngram\": \"no regrets\", \"from\": 4251, \"to\": 4261}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I do not mind what position I end up, as long as I leave the race happy and I did the best I could do.\", \"from\": 4263, \"to\": 4365, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"what position\", \"from\": 4277, \"to\": 4290}, {\"ngram\": \"the race\", \"from\": 4320, \"to\": 4328}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"As for the future, I do not like thinking too far ahead.\", \"from\": 4367, \"to\": 4424, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the future\", \"from\": 4375, \"to\": 4385}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The task I have got, I do not need to be thinking down the line.\\\"\", \"from\": 4425, \"to\": 4490, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the line\", \"from\": 4480, \"to\": 4488}]}, {\"sentence\": \"MORE ABOUT Have your say... 1 Crime Fight breaks out on Elizabeth line train after youths told to stop vaping by middle-aged passenger Fight breaks out on Elizabeth line after youths told to stop vaping 2 Football Liverpool XI vs Brighton: Starting lineup, confirmed team news, injury latest for Premier League today Liverpool XI vs Brighton: Starting lineup and confirmed team news 3 UK Flights alert: UK issues global travel disruption warning over Donald Trump's Iran war Flights alert: UK issues global travel disruption warning on Iran war 4 Lifestyle Horoscope today: Your daily guide for Saturday, March 21, 2026 Horoscope today: Your daily guide for Saturday, March 21, 2026 5 Football Arsenal XI vs Man City: Confirmed team news, predicted lineup, injury latest for Carabao Cup final Arsenal XI vs Man City: Confirmed team news and predicted lineup\", \"from\": 4492, \"to\": 5370, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4552, \"end\": 4561, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elizabeth_II\", \"score\": 0.7217703009114946, \"rank\": 0.3852240254162364, \"text\": \"Elizabeth\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elizabeth_II\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elizabeth_II\"}, {\"begin\": 4652, \"end\": 4661, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elizabeth_II\", \"score\": 0.7217703009114946, \"rank\": 0.3852240254162364, \"text\": \"Elizabeth\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elizabeth_II\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elizabeth_II\"}